  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe how the sine and cosine functions relate to the concepts of circular motion</item>
<item>Describe the connection between simple harmonic motion and circular motion</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
